to the meeting. In the past. Publications Committee meetings have traditionally included
all members.
But the hypocrisy and happiness of this committee during the present crisis represents no departure from its usual methods. And the covering
fact is, similar problems are bound to refer given
the present Publications Committee structure
which allows a faculty-administration majority.
Under the present system:
1.) One administration member (to advise
